title: Unwanted Sexual Reels
review: Suggested reels are coming up on my feed of women in sexual situations or not wearing a bra/underwear in suggestive situations. I don’t watch reels to begin with or anything related to those types of videos for them to come up. I have friends who have posted that they are also getting those videos suggested. Hiding and reporting sexual content only work’s temporarily and then they get pushed again. Hiding the video doesn’t actually hide the video, it dims it but it’s still clearly visible. Facebook needs to stop allowing these videos to keep being posted and pushed to peoples feeds or there’s going to be issues.
